robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive

Class GrimoireContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive.GrimoireContainer

  • public class GrimoireContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    The Grimoire container.

    Java Containers provide functionality, such as handling web request, provide user authentication, logging, or the connection to a database. GrimoireContainer is used to grab grimoire and apply them to setters.

    Since:
    1.0.0

        Creates a new GrimoireContainer object.
